                  <br>&nbsp; Low gear:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">TIME PILOT CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
